name: Experiment Or Die #12
description: Going through years of photos I've dumped off my phone I often run into things that I have very little idea of where it was or why I really took a picture of it. I take pictures of alot of signs and art amongst other things. This is not a real Zebra... it's a photograph of a picture of a zebra and I think it was in Washington DC...can't say for sure. All I do know is it spoke to me at the time, and it still speaks to me today. IG: Nikejerk
